Coffee Shop Sales Analysis 2025
Project Overview:
This project analyzes 8 months of sales data for a coffee shop. It demonstrates the full data workflow: from cleaning messy Excel files to SQL processing and final visualization in Tableau.

Key Insights:

Total Period Revenue: ~$248,568.

Peak Performance: August was the highest-grossing month ($32,649).

Tools Used: SQL (MySQL), Tableau, Excel.

Skills Demonstrated: > * Data Cleaning & ETL

SQL Queries (Unpivoting data with UNION ALL)

Data Visualization & Dashboarding
